<center><font size=3D"+1"><b>Conversion Tables and Methods to Use when
converting</b></font>

<p><font size=3D"+1"><b>from Metric Units to Metric Units
(weight)</b></font></p>

<p><font size=3D"+1"><b>&nbsp;</b></font></p></center>

<p><table border=3D"1" cellspacing=3D"1" cellpadding=3D"7" width=3D"590">
   <tbody><tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23">
         <p><font size=3D"+1"><b>Gram =96 Length</b></font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1"><b>Kilo =96
         Thousand</b></font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1"><b>Liter =96
         Volume</b></font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1"><b>Milli =96
         Thousand</b></font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23" bgcolor=3D"#FFFFFF">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1"><b>Gram =96
         Mass/Weight</b></font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1"><b>Centi =96
         Hundred</b></font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1"><b>Celsius =96
         Temperature</b></font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"50%" height=3D"23">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1"><b>Deci =96 Ten</b></font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
</tbody></table>
</p>

<h3><center>Measure of Weights</center></h3>

<h3><center>Weight/Mass</center></h3>

<p><table border=3D"1" cellspacing=3D"1" width=3D"623">
   <tbody><tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"38%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1,000 milligrams (mg) =3D </font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"62%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1 gram</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"38%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">10 centigrams =3D</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"62%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">100 milligrams (mg)</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"38%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1 gram (g) =3D</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"62%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1,000 milligrams</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"38%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1,000 grams =3D</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"62%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1 kilogram (kg) =3D 1,000,000
         mg</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"38%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1,000 kilograms =3D</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"62%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">1,000,000 grams</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
</tbody></table>
</p>

<h3><center>Operations for Weight</center></h3>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><font size=3D"+1"><b>Example</b>: To get Milligrams from grams you
multiply the grams by 1000</font></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><font size=3D"+1"><b>You Have</b>: 23 grams</font></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><font size=3D"+1"><b>You want milligrams</b>: <b>So, <u> </u>
milligrams =3D <u> 23 </u> Grams</b></font></p>

<p><font size=3D"+1"><b>We Multiply the grams by 1000</b>: 23g x 1000 =3D 2=
3000mg</font></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><font size=3D"+1"><b>You want milligrams</b>: <b>So, <u> </u>
milligrams =3D <u> 23 </u> Grams</b></font></p>

<p>There are 23000 milligrams in 23 grams or 1000 milligrams for every
gram.</p>

<center><table border=3D"1" cellspacing=3D"1" width=3D"636">
   <tbody><tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"31%">
         <p>&nbsp;</p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1"><b>If you have
         this</b></font></center>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"40%">
         <p>&nbsp;</p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1"><b>Do this</b></font></center>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"29%">
         <p>&nbsp;</p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1"><b>To get this</b></font></center>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"31%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">milligrams (mg)</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"40%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Divide by 10 (mg/10)</font></p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1">Move Decimal one place to
         Left</font></center>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"29%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">centigram (cg)</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"31%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">centigrams (cg)</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"40%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Multiply by 10 (cg * 10)</font></p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1">Move decimal one place to the
         right</font></center>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"29%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Milligrams (mg)</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"31%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Grams (g)</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"40%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Multiply by 100 (g *
         100)</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"29%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Centigrams (cg)</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"31%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Centigrams (cm)</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"40%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Divide by 100 (cg/100)</font></p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1">Move decimal two places to the
         left.</font></center>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"29%">
         <p>&nbsp;</p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1">Grams (g)</font></center>
      </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"31%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Milligrams (mg)</font></p>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"40%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Divide by 1000 (mg/1000)</font></p>
        =20
         <center><font size=3D"+1">Move decimal three places to the
         left.</font></center>
      </td>
      <td valign=3D"top" width=3D"29%">
         <p>&nbsp;<font size=3D"+1">Grams (g)</font></p>
      </td>
   </tr>
</tbody></table>
